The paper discusses the properties of complex patterns associated with learned concepts in neural networks, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a prior to regulate learning, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper experiments with fine-grained categories, which is a topic related to natural language processing (cs.CL).
